# isEmpty

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that indicates whether two or three of the dimensions are zero.

## Declaration

```swift
var isEmpty: Bool { get }
```

## Checking characteristics

- **contains(anyOf:)**: Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether the rectangle contains any of the specified points.
- **intersects(_:)**: Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether two rectangles intersect.
